title: #2095 - Moshe Kasher
description: Listen to this episode from The Joe Rogan Experience on Spotify. Moshe Kasher is a stand-up comic, actor, writer, and co-host of podcast "The Endless Honeymoon" with Natasha Leggero. His latest book, "Subculture Vulture: A Memoir in Six Scenes," is available now. www.moshekasher.com
